Package: VerticalCR
Type: Package
Title: Vertical Competing Risks Models with Thresholds and Frailty
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2026-06-03
Authors@R:
    person("Bing", "Wang",
           email = "bingwang@ahu.edu.cn",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits frailty-assisted vertical competing risks models with
    threshold effects using smoothed hierarchical likelihood and adjusted
    profile likelihood calculations. The package includes two-cause model
    fitting utilities, sum-to-zero frailty contrasts, chunked optimization,
    cumulative-incidence prediction, parameter summaries, and efficient score
    threshold-test helpers used in the accompanying manuscript analyses.
